<p class="fd-paragraph">
  A healthcare-native CRM that tracks every patient relationship, interaction history, and engagement signal. Machina's CRM is agent-aware — records update automatically as agents act, keeping data current without manual effort.
</p>

<h2 class="fd-section-heading">What it does</h2>
<ul class="fd-list">
  <li class="fd-list-item">Complete interaction history: calls, texts, tasks, and clinical touchpoints in one timeline</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Engagement scoring based on responsiveness, appointment adherence, and care gap status</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Automatic record updates as agents complete outreach, tasks, and documentation</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Segmentation and cohort tools for population-level campaign management</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="fd-section-heading">Built for value-based care</h2>
<p class="fd-paragraph">
  Generic CRMs weren't designed for healthcare. Machina's CRM understands care gaps, risk scores, and clinical context — making it a tool that actually fits how care teams work.
</p>
